<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Project Summary — {{ repo_name }}</title>
  <style>
    :root { --accent: #7c3aed; --bg: #faf5ff; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: #1e1b4b; margin: 0; padding: 2rem; max-width: 800px; line-height: 1.7; }
    h1 { color: var(--accent); font-size: 2rem; }
    h2 { color: #4c1d95; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.08); margin: 1rem 0; }
    .health-badge { display: inline-block; padding: .4rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 9999px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; }
    .health-high { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
    .health-medium { background: #fef9c3; color: #854d0e; }
    .health-low { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
    .risk-item { border-left: 4px solid #f87171; padding: .75rem 1rem; margin: .75rem 0; background: #fff7f7; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; }
    .action-item { display: flex; gap: .75rem; align-items: flex-start; margin: .6rem 0; }
    .action-num { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 1.75rem; height: 1.75rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: .8rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: .1rem; }
    footer { margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #ddd6fe; padding-top: 1rem; color: #a78bfa; font-size: .8rem; text-align: center; }
    p { color: #4b5563; }
    ul { color: #4b5563; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>📋 Project Summary</h1>
<p style="font-size:.9rem;color:#7c3aed;">{{ repo_url }}</p>

<!-- What It Does -->
<h2>💡 What This Software Does</h2>
<div class="card">
  <p>{{ what_it_does | replace('\n', '<br>') | safe }}</p>
</div>

<!-- How It's Organized -->
<h2>🏗️ How It's Organized</h2>
<div class="card">
  <p>This software has <strong>{{ stats.total_nodes }} components</strong> organized across {{ sections_count }} main areas:</p>
  <ul>
    {% for section, count in sections.items() %}
    <li><strong>{{ section }}</strong> — {{ count }} component{% if count != 1 %}s{% endif %}</li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- Key Components -->
<h2>🔑 Key Components</h2>
<div class="card">
  {% for node in key_components[:5] %}
  <p><strong>Component {{ loop.index }}:</strong> {{ node.ai_summary or "A core system component." }}</p>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<!-- Risk Areas -->
<h2>⚠️ Risk Areas</h2>
{% if risk_areas %}
{% for node in risk_areas[:3] %}
<div class="risk-item">
  <strong>Risk {{ loop.index }}:</strong>
  {{ node.ai_summary[:120] or "This component is frequently changed and carries risk." }}
  <br><small style="color:#9ca3af;">Churn Score: {{ "%.0f"|format(node.churn_score) }}/100 · Bug Commit Ratio: {{ "%.0%"|format(node.bug_commit_ratio) }}</small>
</div>
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
<div class="card"><p>No significant risk areas detected. The codebase appears stable.</p></div>
{% endif %}

<!-- AI Summary -->
<h2>📝 Summary</h2>
<div class="card">
  <p>{{ ai_summary_text | replace('\n', '<br>') | safe }}</p>
</div>

<!-- Recommended Actions -->
<h2>✅ Recommended Actions</h2>
<div class="card">
  <div class="action-item"><div class="action-num">1</div><p>Review the {{ stats.high_impact_count }} high-impact components identified in the detailed technical report — these are the most critical for system stability.</p></div>
  <div class="action-item"><div class="action-num">2</div><p>Investigate the {{ stats.orphan_count }} unused code modules that are not connected to the rest of the system — these may be safe to remove.</p></div>
  <div class="action-item"><div class="action-num">3</div><p>Pay special attention to the {{ stats.hot_zone_count }} files predicted to change soon — ensure they have adequate testing.</p></div>
  <div class="action-item"><div class="action-num">4</div><p>Use the onboarding path from the detailed report to efficiently orient new team members.</p></div>
</div>

<!-- Health Score -->
<h2>💊 Health at a Glance</h2>
<div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
  <p style="font-size:1.1rem;">Overall System Health:</p>
  <span class="health-badge health-{{ health_level.lower() }}">{{ health_level }}</span>
  <p style="margin-top:1rem;">{{ health_explanation }}</p>
</div>

<footer>
  Generated by git-filter | {{ generated_at }} | For non-technical stakeholders.
</footer>
</body>
</html>
